quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Nahin mai kasam khata hoon is shehar(city) ki
  90,2,Aur haal yeh hai ke (Aey nabi) is shehar mein tumko halal kar liya gaya hai
  90,3,Aur kasam khata hoon baap(Adam) ki aur us aulad ki jo ussey paida hui
  90,4,Dar haqeeqat humne Insan ko mushakkat mein paida kiya hai
  90,5,Kya usne yeh samajh rakhha hai kay uspar koi qaabu na paa sakega
  90,6,Kehta hai ke maine dhairon maal udaa diya
  90,7,Kya woh samajhta hai kay kisi ne usko nahin dekha
  90,8,Kya humne usey do aankhein
  90,9,Aur ek zubaan aur do honth nahin diye
  90,10,Aur dono numayan raste usey (nahin) dikha diye
  90,11,Magar usne dushwar guzar ghati(steep) se guzarne ki himmat na ki
  90,12,Aur tum kya jaano kay kya hai woh dushwar guzar ghaati
  90,13,Kisi gardan ko gulami se chudana
  90,14,Ya faake ke din
  90,15,kisi qareebi yateem
  90,16,Ya khaak nasheen miskeen ko khana khilana
  90,17,Phir (iske saath yeh kay) aadmi un logon mein shamil ho jo imaan laye aur jinhon ne ek dusrey ko sabr aur (khalq-e-khuda par) raham ki talqeen ki
  90,18,Yeh log hain dayein baazu(right hand) waley
  90,19,Aur jinhon ne hamari aayat ko mann-ney se inkar kiya woh bayen bazu(left hand) waley hain
  90,20,Un par aag chaayi hui hogi
  91,1,Suraj aur uski dhoop ki kasam
  91,2,Aur Chand ki kasam jabke wo uske pichey aata hai
  91,3,Aur din ki kasam jabke woh (Suraj ko) numaya kar deta hai
  91,4,Aur raat ki kasam jabke woh (suraj ko) dhank leti hai
  91,5,Aur aasman ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey qayam kiya
  91,6,Aur zameen ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey bichaya
  91,7,Aur nafs-e-Insani ki aur us zaat ki kasam jisne usey hamwar kiya
  91,8,Phir uski badi aur uski parhezgari uss par ilham kar di
  91,9,Yaqeenan falah pa gaya woh jisne nafs ka tazkiya kiya
  91,10,Aur na-murad hua woh jisne usko daba diya
  91,11,Samood ne apni sarkashi ki bina par jhutlaya
  91,12,Jab us qaum ka sab se zyada shaqi (Badnaseeb) aadmi biphar kar utha
  91,13,To Allah ke Rasool ne un logon se kaha ke khabardar Allah ki ountni (she-camel) ko (haath na lagana) aur uske paani peene (mein maane na hona)
  91,14,Magar unhon ne uski baat ko jhuta qarar diya aur ountni ko maar dala. Aakhir-e-kaar unke gunah ke padash mein unke Rubb ne unpar aisi aafat toodi ke ek saath sab ko paywand-e-khaaq kar diya
  91,15,Aur usey (apne is fail kay) kisi burey natije ka koi khauf(darr) nahin hai
  92,1,Kasam hai raat ki jabke woh chaa jaaye
  92,2,Aur din ki jabke woh roshan ho
  92,3,Aur us zaat ki jisne nar(male) aur maada(female) ko paida kiya
  92,4,Dar haqeeqat tum logon ki koshishein mukhtalif qism ki hai
  92,5,To jisne (rah e khuda mein) maal diya aur (khuda ki nafarmani se) parhez kiya
  92,6,Aur bhalayi ko sach mana
  92,7,Usko hum aasan raastey kay liye sahulat denge
  92,8,Aur jisne bukhl(kanjoosi) kiya aur (apney khuda se) be niyazi(self-sufficient/independent) barti
  92,9,aur bhalayi ko jhutlaya
  92,10,Usko hum sakht rastey kay liye sahulat dengey
  92,11,Aur uska maal aakhir uske kis kaam aayega jabke woh halaq ho jaye
  92,12,Beshak rasta batana hamare zimmey hai
  92,13,aur dar haqeeqat aakhirat aur duniya dono kay hum hi malik hai
  92,14,Pas maine tumko khabardar kar diya hai bhadakti hui aag se
  92,15,Usmein nahin jhulsega magar woh intihayi badbakth
  92,16,jisne jhutlaya aur mooh phera
  92,17,Aur usse door rakkha jayega woh nihayat parhezgaar
  92,18,Jo paakiza honay ki khatir apna maal deta hai
  92,19,Uspar kisi ka koi ehsan nahin hai jiska badla usey dena ho
  92,20,Woh to sirf apne Rubb-e-bartrar ki raza joii ke liye yeh kaam karta hai
  92,21,Aur zaroor woh (us se) khush hoga
  93,1,Kasam hai rozey roshan ki
  93,2,Aur raat ki jabke woh sukoon ke saath taari ho jaye
  93,3,(Aey nabi) tumharey Rubb ne tumko hargiz nahin chodha aur na woh naraaz hua
  93,4,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liya baad ka daur pehle daur se behtar hai
  93,5,Aur anqareeb tumhra Rubb tumko itna dega ke tum khush ho jaogey
  93,6,Kya usne tumko yateem nahin paya aur phir thikana faraham kiya
  93,7,Aur tumhey nawaqif-e-raah paya aur phir hidayat bakshi
  93,8,Aur tumhein nadaar(in want) paya aur phir maldar kar diya
  93,9,Lihaza yateem par sakhti na karo
  93,10,Aur saayil(maangne waley) ko na jhidko
  93,11,Aur apne Rubb ki niyamt ka izhar karo